@startuml
title Online Quiz System State Machine Diagram

state Start <<choice>>
state RegisterState
state LoginState <<choice>>
state TeacherChoice <<choice>>
state StudentChoice <<choice>>

state CreateQuiz
state EditQuiz
state SaveDraft
state PostQuiz
state ViewResults

state SelectQuiz
state AnswerQuiz
state SubmitQuiz
state ViewResult

[*] --> Start

Start --> RegisterState : [Register]
Start --> LoginState : [Login]

RegisterState --> LoginState : [Registered]

LoginState --> TeacherChoice : [Teacher]
LoginState --> StudentChoice : [Student]

TeacherChoice --> CreateQuiz : [Create New Quiz]
TeacherChoice --> EditQuiz : [Edit Existing Quiz]
TeacherChoice --> SaveDraft : [Save as Draft]
TeacherChoice --> PostQuiz : [Post Quiz]
TeacherChoice --> ViewResults : [View Results]

StudentChoice --> SelectQuiz : [Select Quiz]
SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz
AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult

CreateQuiz --> TeacherChoice : [Back to Menu]
EditQuiz --> TeacherChoice : [Back to Menu]
SaveDraft --> TeacherChoice : [Back to Menu]
PostQuiz --> TeacherChoice : [Back to Menu]
ViewResults --> TeacherChoice : [Back to Menu]

AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz : [Submit Answers]
SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult : [Submitted]

ViewResult --> [*] : [Logout]
@enduml
